&lt;p&gt;If you can relate to the&amp;nbsp;&lt;a href=&quot;https://about.paypay.ne.jp/career/en/work-style/&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;&quot;PayPay 5 senses&quot;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/a&gt;which are important work values for PayPay Card employees, you will surely enjoy working in this environment! Let&#39;s create the No.1 FinTech company together!&lt;/p&gt;
